---
// Purpose-Built Capabilities section for Professional Services industry page
---

<section id="capabilities" class="cre-capabilities-section">
  <div class="cre-capabilities-container">
    <span class="section-label">PURPOSE-BUILT CAPABILITIES</span>
    <h2 class="cre-capabilities-headline">
      Professional services systems engineered for your workflow
    </h2>

    <div class="cre-capabilities-grid">
      <!-- Deal Sourcing -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-1.webp" alt="Project Scoping & Planning" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Project Scoping & Planning</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Automated project scoping that captures requirements, defines deliverables, and tracks scope through delivery. Creates unified project baseline that all teams reference, eliminating scope creep and serving as basis for profitability tracking.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Structured scope capture workflow</li>
            <li>Deliverable definition and tracking</li>
            <li>Scope change management</li>
            <li>Risk and assumption logging</li>
            <li>Baselined project parameters</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Underwriting -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-5.webp" alt="Resource Allocation & Planning" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Resource Allocation & Planning</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Intelligent resource planning that matches available consultants to project requirements, forecasts team capacity, and automatically adjusts allocations as projects evolve. Maximizes billable utilization while preventing overallocation.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Resource availability tracking</li>
            <li>Skill-based resource matching</li>
            <li>Capacity forecasting</li>
            <li>Automated allocation workflows</li>
            <li>Utilization analytics by consultant and project</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Portfolio Analytics -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-6.webp" alt="Time Tracking & Project Actuals" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Time Tracking & Project Actuals</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Automated time tracking that captures billable hours at project, task, and activity level. Provides real-time visibility into project spend versus budget and surfaces variances before projects go over.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Activity-based time capture</li>
            <li>Project spend tracking</li>
            <li>Budget variance monitoring</li>
            <li>Time export for billing</li>
            <li>Consultant productivity analytics</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Investor Reporting -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-2.webp" alt="Project Performance & Profitability" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Project Performance & Profitability</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Real-time project dashboards that track budget utilization, team productivity, schedule status, and margin realization. Identify projects at risk before they impact firm profitability.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Project budget tracking</li>
            <li>Margin realization reporting</li>
            <li>Schedule performance analysis</li>
            <li>Team productivity by project</li>
            <li>Project profitability forecasting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Buyer Profile Management -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-3.webp" alt="Client Collaboration & Delivery" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Client Collaboration & Delivery</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Unified client workspace that centralizes project communication, deliverables, feedback, and approvals. Reduces email sprawl and ensures stakeholders have single source of truth for project status.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Centralized project communication</li>
            <li>Deliverable repository and versioning</li>
            <li>Client approval workflows</li>
            <li>Feedback and change request tracking</li>
            <li>Project timeline and milestone visibility</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Market Intelligence -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-7.webp" alt="Billing & Revenue Recognition" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Billing & Revenue Recognition</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Automated billing that generates invoices from tracked time, project expenses, and milestone billings without manual work. Reduces billing cycles and improves cash flow.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Automated invoice generation</li>
            <li>Multi-billing-model support</li>
            <li>Expense tracking and billing</li>
            <li>Milestone-based billing workflows</li>
            <li>Client payment tracking</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-capabilities-section {
    background: #0052CC;
    color: #ffffff;
    width: 100vw;
    margin: 0;
    margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
    padding: clamp(40px, 5vw, 60px) 24px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .cre-capability-card {
    background: transparent;
    border: 3px solid #ffffff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cre-capability-icon {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .cre-capability-icon img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
  }

  .cre-capability-title {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  }

  .cre-capability-description {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .cre-includes-section {
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .cre-includes-section strong {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .cre-includes-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cre-includes-list li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    padding: 4px 0 4px 16px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .cre-includes-list li::before {
    content: "â€¢";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .cre-capability-icon {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-capabilities-section {
      padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px) 24px;
    }

    .cre-capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cre-capability-card {
      padding: 28px 20px;
      border: 2px solid #ffffff;
    }

    .cre-capability-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }

    .cre-capability-title {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .cre-capability-description {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .cre-includes-list li {
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  }
</style>

